caption.p: Enriched biological processes after treatment of hTCEpi cells with AC EFs for 24 h. Significantly enriched biological processes following analysis of the antibody array data are highlighted as an interactive hierarchical clustering tree using ShinyGO. Biological processes with many shared genes are clustered together. Bigger dots indicate more significant p-values. Enriched biological processes that were similar after analysis of both gene and protein array data are marked and highlighted. Analysis was performed using ShinyGO (v.0.61) (Available online: http://bioinformatics.sdstate.edu/go/ (accessed 6 January 2021)).
